From 96320ab6c1d57d4eb44381f5a9dc85ceb7d2cb6a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Riajul Islam <opensource@example.com>
Date: Sun, 5 Apr 2026 09:02:26 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add Zoho sign-in button to OAuth dialog

Add ZohoLogo SVG component, extend OAuthProvider type with 'zoho',
and add "Continue with Zoho" button to the sign-in dialog.
Includes i18n translations for all supported locales.
---
